CHANGES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        o
    ____|____
   |         |  This file lists changes made to the Ansible role.
   |  _   _  |  The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and
   | [_] [_] |  formatted to allow easy grepping by scripts.
   |____~____|
    ___//__//   The fields are:
   /|     |/    B: bug
  //|_____|     F: feature
    _|| ||_     I: improvement
   (__| |__)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.2.6 (2015-11-08)
I: Improve 'group_vars' and 'host_vars' options

* Version 0.2.5 (2014-12-14)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.2.4 (2014-11-14)
I: Remove needless 'when' statements

* Version 0.2.3 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.2.2 (2014-08-22)
I: Ensure Ansible role is OS agnostic

* Version 0.2.1 (2014-08-20)
B: Add missing loopback connection
B: Remove obsolete file only required for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.1.3 (2014-08-14)
I: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.1.2 (2014-06-30)
B: Fix issue with handlers

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-05-10)
B: Fix issue with reloading IPtables rules

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-04-26)
F: Initial release
